upgrade
Discworld Creator help
upgrade

.SH Name
.SI 5
upgrade - Logs off and immediately logs back on
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
upgrade
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Upgrade performs a quit and relogs you in as though you had done it yourself
except that it does not disconnect you from the mud in the process.  
A save is performed so no information is lost.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
quit, su
.EP
